--- !u!114 &11400050
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 1
  m_PrefabParentObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInternal: {fileID: 100100000}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 100040}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9d0b5f3bbe925a408bd595c79d0bf63, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  mPivot: 0
  mWidth: 470
  mHeight: 4160
  mDepth: 0
  autoResizeBoxCollider: 0
  keepCrispWhenShrunk: 1
  mTrueTypeFont: {fileID: 10102, guid: 0000000000000000e000000000000000, type: 0}
  mFont: {fileID: 0}
  mText: "[Privacy Policy]\r\n1. Information We Collect\r\n- User accounts : You may
    be required to open an account directly with Ticket Space by completing the registration
    process and providing true, accurate, current and complete information about yourself.
    \ Personal information may also be required to use or participate in certain Services,
    such as registering for games, prize acceptance, customer support and/or technical
    service requests, marketing surveys and email campaigns, product and service orders,
    and requests from third party service providers. Information collected will vary
    depending upon the activity and may include (1) account information (email ID),
    (2) your profile (profile picture, game user name, and other biographic details
    such as gender, birth year) (3) Shopping(Delivery) Information (your name, email
    address, Mobile Phone number, phone number, home address, game user name(Nickname),
    country information. You may also complete a user profile that can be viewed by
    other users of the Services, which may include a profile picture, game user name(Nickname),
    and other biographic details(gender, birth year) you provide.\r\n- Mobile devices
    : Information collected from users of the Mobile Game App may include the mobile
    phone number, the mobile device identifier, IP address, the name associated with
    the device, the identity of the mobile carrier, the mobile phone model, country,
    geo-location and email address.  We may create and assign an account number or
    ID to your mobile device. You may allow us to send push notifications and local
    notifications to your mobile device with game updates and other messages.  These
    notifications can be adjusted on your mobile device settings or through the Mobile
    Game App.\r\n- Social networking websites : The Services may be offered to you
    through a social networking website through which you may access this Site.  You
    may be able to use your user account or user ID from the social networking website.
    \ By accessing or using a game, application, or activity on this Site, you may
    be granting the social networking website permission to share your e-mail address
    and any other personal information with us, including name, address, gender, age,
    profile picture and information, occupation, hobbies, interests, and zip code.
    When you access and use the Services through on a social networking website, we
    may collect information regarding your use, as well as other information from
    your social networking website profile in accordance with the website's terms
    of use.  If we provide you the ability to import your address book contacts to
    invite them to join you in using the Services, if you invite someone into your
    social network , or if you send messages through the Services, we may also collect
    and maintain the information associated with those messages, including your contact\u2019s
    email address, ID number and any content. \r\n- Billing information : You may
    be required to pay for certain Services, including an exchange for Virtual Tickets.
    Current, complete, and accurate information for your billing account is required
    and you must also promptly update all information, such as a change in billing
    or shipping address, credit card number, or credit card expiration date.\r\n-
    Content : You may make your personal information available when you are allowed
    or invited to share or participate in games, blogs, message boards, online forums
    and other functionality.  The Services may also provide you with the opportunity
    to create, submit, post, display, transmit, perform, publish, distribute or broadcast
    content and materials to Ticket Space Games and/or to or through this Site or
    the Mobile Game App.  This may include text, writings, graphics, comments, forum
    posts, chat posts, communications, messages, profiles, personally identifiable
    information, suggestions, links, e-mails, music, sound, graphics, images, pictures,
    video, software, technology, code and other material and information perceived,
    made available, or emanating to and/or from the Services (collectively, \"Content\").
    Content also includes any feedback, comments, or suggestions you may provide regarding
    the Services, other Content, this Site, or the Mobile Game App, including any
    responses provided through user surveys.\r\n2. Use of Information \r\nWe may use
    information about you for various purposes, including to:\r\n-\tProvide, maintain
    and improve our Services;\r\n-\tProvide and deliver the products and services
    you request and send you related information, including confirmations and invoices;
    \r\n-\tSend you communications about products, services, offers, promotions, rewards,
    and events offered by Ticket Space and other companies, and provide news and information
    we think will be of interest to you; \r\n-\tSend you technical notices, updates,
    security alerts and support and administrative messages;\r\n-\tRespond to your
    comments, questions and requests and provide customer service;\r\n-\tMonitor and
    analyze trends, usage and activities in connection with our Services; \r\n-\tPersonalize
    and improve the Services and provide advertisements, content, suggested connections
    or features that match user profiles or activities; \r\n-\tProcess and deliver
    contest entries and rewards;\r\n-\tLink or combine with information we get from
    others to help understand your needs and provide you with better service; and\r\n-\tCarry
    out any other purpose for which the information was collected.\r\n-\tTicket Space
    is based in the South Korea and the information we collect is governed by South
    Korea law.  By accessing or using the Services or otherwise providing information
    to us, you consent to the processing and transfer of information in and to the
    South Korea and other countries.\r\n3. Sharing Information \r\nWe will not share
    or disclose your personal information to any third parties without your consent.
    \ However, we may disclose information about you to third party contractors in
    order to provide the Services, to resolve service problems, to correct errors
    in the Services, to communicate with you, to provide you with advertising and
    promotional information in connection with the Services, and to enhance your experience
    on this Site or your mobile device.  Third party contractors may also use your
    personal information to provide email delivery, product, prize or promotional
    fulfillment, contest administration, credit card processing, shipping or other
    Services.  When requesting these Services, you may be asked to provide your personal
    information, including your name, mailing address, telephone number and email
    address.  When the third party contractors have access to the personal information
    that you provide to us, we require them to adhere to our privacy policies and
    to protect the confidentiality of your personal information while performing their
    duties for us. These third parties are prohibited from using your personal information
    for any other purpose without your specific consent.\r\n4. Special Notice Regarding
    Children Under 10 Years of Age\r\nThese Services are not aimed at nor intended
    for children under the age of 10. If you are under the age of 10, please do not
    use the Services, and if you are over the age of 10 but under the age of 18, you
    should use the Services only with the and permission and/or supervision of a parent
    or legal guardian. Our Services do not accept registration from children under
    the age of 10. No personal information is purposefully or knowingly collected
    from children under the age of 10 by Ticket Space. Parents are hereby put on notice
    that as a result of the foregoing, Ticket Space does not provide a mechanism to
    obtain parental consent. \r\nIf you are a parent or guardian who has discovered
    that your child has submitted his or her personal information to Ticket Space,
    Ticket Space will make commercially reasonable efforts to delete the information
    from its database, at your request. To request the deletion of your child's information,
    please send an email to (ticketspace-as@ulike.co.kr) and be sure to include in
    your message the same member name and password that your child submitted. Your
    use of the Services indicates that you hereby represent and warrant that all information
    you provide, including but not limited to age, shall be truthful and correct.\r\n5.
    Information Security\r\nThe security of your personal information is important
    to us.  We follow generally accepted industry standards to protect the personal
    information submitted to us, both during transmission and in storage. When you
    send sensitive information (such as a credit card number) we encrypt that information
    using secure socket layer technology (SSL).  However, no method of data transmission
    over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. Therefore, while
    we strive to use commercially reasonable means to protect your personal information,
    we cannot guarantee its absolute security.\r\n6. Changes to Privacy Policy\r\nWe
    reserve the right to change this Privacy Policy in any way and at any time.  We
    will attempt to give you advance notice of any change in this Privacy Policy by
    posting on this Site or the Mobile Game App , or by sending a message informing
    you of the modified terms with a link to the posting on this Site or the Mobile
    Game App.  However, we reserve the right to make changes immediately, as determined
    in our sole discretion.  You agree to periodically check this Site or the Mobile
    Game App and to read any changes to this Privacy Policy.  Using our Services after
    any changes to this Privacy Policy become effective constitutes your acceptance
    of the new Privacy Policy.  If you do not agree to this Privacy Policy or any
    future changes to this Privacy Policy, you do not have permission to use the Services
    and you must immediately discontinue any further use of the Services.\r\n7. Contact
    Us\r\nTicket Space AS Email: ticketspace-as@ulike.co.kr\r\n"
  mFontSize: 20
  mFontStyle: 0
  mEncoding: 1
  mMaxLineCount: 0
  mEffectStyle: 0
  mEffectColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 1}
  mSymbols: 1
  mEffectDistance: {x: 1, y: 1}
  mOverflow: 3
  mShrinkToFit: 0
